body.name: Wireless Keyboard and Mouse, XTREMTEC 2.4G Full Size Wireless Keyboard Mouse Combo - Ultra Slim Silent Cute Computer Keyboard with USB Receiver for Windows, OS, PC, Desktop, Mac, Tablet (Purple)
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Thursday, February 15. Order within 12 hrs 32 mins
features: 🟣[RETRO ROUND KEYBOARD DESIGN]: Vintage typewriter-inspired rounded keycaps offer you visual enjoyment and please you with every single press & click. The ergonomic slope design of the purple keyboard gives you the most comfortable typing experience.

🟣[PLUG and PLAY 2.4G WIRELESS KEYBOARD MOUSE]: Just insert the ONLY 1 nano USB receiver (stored inside the keyboard, NOT inside the mouse) into your computer and use the keyboard and mouse instantly. 1 USB Receiver Can Connect Both Keyboard and Mouse.

🟣[ULTRA-SLIM COMPUTER KEYBOARDS]: ABS material used, the wireless keyboard and mouse combo is not only of a cute retro keyboard wireless style but also unexpectedly lightweight, making it easy to carry on the go. The thinnest part is 0.4cm.

🟣[QUIET KEYBOARD MOUSE COMBO]: Noise-reduced scissor-cross Cute Round-Key best suit working in a quiet environment. Also, you will fall in love with the smooth touch of the optical mouse and the matte-like surface of each key.

🟣[LONG BATTERY LIFE(NOT INCLUDE BATTERY)]: Both purple wireless keyboard and mouse feature auto sleeping mode once you stop using the cute keyboards for 5 sec, they work with a lower current to save energy. You can click any key to wake up them.

🟣[WIDE COMPATIBILITY]: The cordless keyboard and mouse combo are compatible with Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8, 10 systems, Mac iOS, and other USB devices, which means they work perfectly with your PCs, Laptop, Smart TV, desktop computer, or notebook, etc.

🟣[DURABLE KEYS & FREE SILICONE COVER]: The round keys can be pressed up to 3 million times. The letters are not stickers, it is anti-scratched UV coating. Free soft silicone cover will protect your laptop keyboard from dust and scratches.

🟣[FULL-SIZE WIRELESS KEYBOARDS]: This Full-size keyboard with a numeric keypad has a tilt angle for a great typing position. The ergonomic wireless mouse would provide hrs of work comfortably. NOTE: The hotkeys are not fully compatible with Mac System.

NOTE: There is only ONE nano USB receiver for Both the Keyboard and Mouse. The nano USB receiver is stored inside the battery case of the keyboard. The slot in the mouse is only for storing it and does not contain anything when you first open it.
WHAT YOU GET: 1 * XTREMTEC Purple wireless keyboard, 1*wireless mouse, 1* nano USB receiver, 1*Type -C adapter, 1* Silicon cover, 1*user manual

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: i love this keyboard, im a cad tech so i need a good keyboard and mouse to get a lot of use out of. ive gotten multiple compliments on it and its a super cute color. It comes with a silicone cover to put over the buttons for everyday use and i love it. im actually wearing it down and would love to buy just another silicone matt to replace this one. keeps me from getting my keys stuck with dirt and dust and still get the full color and cuteness of the keyboard. O! the mouse is perfect too, i have smaller hands and cant with the bulky mouses so this one is perfect! will update with pictures later!EDIT: After about 11 months the mouse isn't working. i keep it clean, change out the batteries and have a pretty clean station so idk why its not working, it seems like the laser on the bottom isnt good anymore, time to get a new mouse. Keyboard is still working great though!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Keyboard works great. However the mouse turns off after like 20 seconds to save battery. So there’s definitely a lot of lag whenever you go to double check paperwork or take a sip of water. Super frustrating. I ended up getting rid of the mouse, keeping the keyboard and just using a lodgitec mouse instead. UPDATE: seller offered to fix my issue so I’m changing this from 3 to 5 stars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So pretty! Very aesthetic looking on my work desk! 🥹🫶🏼
reviews.reviewText: This keyboard and mouse is one of the good product finds I bought from amazon! I bought this mainly because of the color 🤣 I love color purple and I thought it would look pretty on my purple room and work from home station and I’m sure it did cause look at it! So pretty 🥹 though I’m a little bit disappointed cause the copy and paste function doesn’t work on this keyboard. I’m using a MacBook Air M2. I was also expecting the free usb to usb-c converter cause it’s included in the product description but got a matching keyboard protector for it. It was nice though to keep the dust away from my keyboard. Anyway thank you! Just half regret buying it because I’m very disappointed that the copy and paste function doesn’t work, I use it all the time for my work and now I will have a hard time because I can’t use the copy and paste function 🫤
The color is just so cute! It's so quiet when I type and the mouse makes minimal clicking noises. Love the silicone keyboard protection as well! Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewText: Very pretty but it is the loudest mouse I have used in a long time. It took me a while to get used to how loud is the clicking. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on July 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: Good keyboard, but needs more attention to detail
reviews.reviewText: I love the colour of this keyboard and how smooth the keys are. The mouse is also very comfortable to hold and has a side peice to put your thumb when in use.My main issue is that there are a key keys labelled as a symbol but are not actually that symbol so it can become slightly confusing when you're typing.It could also so with having the option to tilt it (I don't know how to articulate how I mean); for example. how some keyboards have the tabs on the back so you can raise it. That would be extremely beneficial so as to prevent repetitive strain injuries and also reduce the stress on carpal tunnel syndrome.I do love the aesthetic though and it's very light weight and simple to set up.
It is amazing and so quiet when typing and using the mouse.
